Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Oil rationing threat
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bx30
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Feb 1979
Threat of oil rationing as Ayatollah Khomeini takes over as Iran leader. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.